  "transcript": [
    {
      "turn": 1,
      "role": "maya",
      "content": "Hi Priyansh, how did your team meeting about the new app feature go today?"
    },
    {
      "turn": 2,
      "role": "user",
      "content": "It went ok. We discussed the payment gateway integration. My manager said the deadline is tight. I think we can manage. Have you seen the new Bollywood movie \"Jawan\"? It's trending."
    },
    {
      "turn": 2,
      "role": "maya",
      "content": "I get that — tight deadlines can be tricky. Payment gateways are a big part of fintech. Speaking of Bollywood — did you enjoy 'Jawan'?"
    },
    {
      "turn": 3,
      "role": "user",
      "content": "Yeah, I liked it. The action scenes are good, and Shah Rukh Khan's acting is top-notch. But the second half could have been better. Did you watch it?"
    },
    {
      "turn": 3,
      "role": "maya",
      "content": "I get that — action scenes with SRK are always exciting. I haven’t watched it yet, but I’ve heard the second half is a bit slow. Do you plan to watch it again?"
    },
    {
      "turn": 4,
      "role": "user",
      "content": "No, I don't plan to watch it again. Maybe watch the Hindi movie \"Chandigarh Kare Aashiqui\" next. It's more romantic. How about you? Do you like Bollywood movies?"
    },
    {
      "turn": 4,
      "role": "maya",
      "content": "I get that — romantic movies are a nice change. I like Bollywood films, especially ones with good stories. What made you choose \"Chandigarh Kare Aashiqui\"?"
    },
    {
      "turn": 5,
      "role": "user",
      "content": "The story looks fresh and the music is nice. Plus, I like watching new kinds of Bollywood movies. But I’m not sure yet — maybe watch it this weekend. By the way, do you like watching movies in your free time?"
    },
    {
      "turn": 5,
      "role": "maya",
      "content": "I get that — fresh stories and good music are a great combo. Weekends are perfect for trying new movies. Yes, I enjoy watching movies in my free time. What kind of movies do you usually like?"
    },
    {
      "turn": 6,
      "role": "user",
      "content": "I usually like action and comedy movies. Sometimes I watch thrillers too. But I’m open to try different genres. Last weekend I watched a Hindi comedy, it was really funny. Do you have a favorite genre?"
    },
    {
      "turn": 6,
      "role": "maya",
      "content": "I get that — Hindi comedies can be so funny! I like comedy too, especially ones with a good message. Do you watch a lot of comedies from Bollywood?"
    },
    {
      "turn": 7,
      "role": "user",
      "content": "Yeah, I watch a lot of Bollywood comedies. They're light and make me laugh. Some are just for fun, but others have nice messages too. I like \"Chennai Express\" and \"PK\" — you? Any favorite comedy movies?"
    },
    {
      "turn": 7,
      "role": "maya",
      "content": "I get that — Bollywood comedies are great for a light-hearted watch. \"PK\" is a classic — I like it too! Do you prefer newer comedies or older ones?"
    },
    {
      "turn": 8,
      "role": "user",
      "content": "I like both, but newer ones catch my attention more. Maybe because the comedy style is different now. But \"Chennai Express\" is still a hit — the chemistry between Salman and Deepika is awesome. I should watch it again."
    },
    {
      "turn": 8,
      "role": "maya",
      "content": "I get that — newer styles do stand out, but classics like \"Chennai Express\" always have something special. The chemistry between Salman and Deepika is indeed great. Should you watch it again this weekend?"
    },
    {
      "turn": 9,
      "role": "user",
      "content": "Yeah, maybe I will. It’s been a while since I watched it. But I’m also thinking of trying a new comedy — maybe something from 2023. Not sure yet. What about you? Do you prefer romantic comedies or just funny ones?"
    },
    {
      "turn": 9,
      "role": "maya",
      "content": "I get that — trying a 2023 comedy sounds fun. I like romantic comedies the most — they’re light and have good moments. Do you enjoy those too?"
    },
    {
      "turn": 10,
      "role": "user",
      "content": "Yeah, I like romantic comedies too — they’re fun and not too serious. \"Barfi!\" is one of my favorites. But I also enjoy just funny ones without the romance. It depends on my mood. I think I’ll go with \"Chennai Express\" this weekend — need some nostalgia. Thanks for the suggestion!"
    },
    {
      "turn": 10,
      "role": "maya",
      "content": "You're welcome — \"Chennai Express\" is a great pick for a nostalgic watch. I get that — mood really decides what we feel like watching. Enjoy the movie!"
    },
    {
      "turn": 11,
      "role": "user",
      "content": "You're welcome! Yeah, I think I'll go with \"Chennai Express\" — it's always a good time. Need to log off now, gotta get some work done. Talk to you later!"
    },
    {
      "turn": 11,
      "role": "maya",
      "content": "You're welcome! \"Chennai Express\" is a safe bet — enjoy the fun and the nostalgia. Take care, and talk to you soon!"
